[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":1451},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fjavascript\u002F20211219\u002F3830068067\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fjavascript\u002F20211219\u002F3830068067\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fjavascript\u002F20211219\u002F3830068067\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fjavascript\u002F20211219\u002F3830068067\u002F":1427,"related:\u002Fjavascript\u002F20211219\u002F3830068067\u002F":1436},"\u002Fen\u002Fjavascript\u002F2021\u002F12\u002F19\u002Ffunctional-programming-in-javascript-intro\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":1411,"date":1412,"description":24,"extension":1413,"lang":1414,"meta":1415,"navigation":132,"path":1416,"readingMinutes":1417,"seo":1418,"standalone":1419,"stem":1420,"tags":1421,"tldr":1423,"updated":1424,"url":1425,"__hash__":1426},"content\u002FJavaScript\u002F簡單趣談-Functional-Programming-in-JavaScript.md","簡單趣談 Functional Programming in JavaScript","3830068067",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":1398},"minimark",[11,18,22,25,29,32,35,38,44,47,55,160,166,179,182,220,223,243,249,258,262,265,272,277,280,342,352,356,359,415,418,421,426,430,433,436,527,530,627,634,714,722,726,729,740,826,831,924,931,1021,1024,1028,1031,1061,1067,1102,1111,1176,1187,1190,1269,1275,1364,1367,1377,1380,1394],[12,13,14],"p",{},[15,16],"img",{"alt":6,"src":17},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fjavascript\u002Ffp-currying\u002Fisray_notarray_Functional_Programming_--stylize_750_--v_5.2_0eedf977-bd19-4b52-b450-99f7a8125b4e.png",[19,20,21],"h2",{"id":21},"前言",[12,23,24],{},"Functional Programming 可以說是一個非常好玩的設計模式，為什麼需要 Functional Programming 的設計模式呢？簡單來講就是要避免一些問題 (Side Effect)，所以就乾脆寫一篇很入門的、很簡單的 Functional Programming in JavaScript。",[19,26,28],{"id":27},"side-effect-副作用","Side Effect (副作用)",[12,30,31],{},"開始介紹 Functional Programming 之前，我想先聊一些東西，第一個也就是 Side Effect。",[12,33,34],{},"什麼是 Side Effect 呢？Side Effect 中文稱之為「副作用」，副作用這一詞，非常常見在一個地方，也就是你看醫生後所拿到的感冒藥會有哪些副作用，例如：頭痛、嗜睡以及身體痠痛等這些副作用。",[12,36,37],{},"但是 Side Effect 本身也可以說是有幫助的、有益處的，只是大多都會用來形容不良的反應居多，例如你吃了感冒藥用的副作用有感冒好轉以及嗜睡等。",[39,40,41],"blockquote",{},[12,42,43],{},"副作用不代表壞的，也有好的意思。",[12,45,46],{},"所以你可以把 Side Effect 理解成「當你執行某個函式或是行為時，會導致原有的狀態被修改或附加功能」，這些就稱之為 Side Effect，例如：全域變數被修改或者是輸出一個系統訊息等等，這些都算是一個 Side Effect。",[12,48,49,50,54],{},"這時候你應該會覺得很奇妙，為什麼輸出訊息 (",[51,52,53],"code",{},"console.log()",") 也會算是一個 Side Effect 呢？我們來看一段範例程式碼，或許你會更清楚一點",[56,57,62],"pre",{"className":58,"code":59,"language":60,"meta":61,"style":61},"language-js shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","function sayHello(name) {\n  console.log('Say');\n  return 'Hello' + name;;\n}\n\nsayHello('Ray');\n\u002F\u002F Say\n\u002F\u002F Hello Ray\n","js","",[51,63,64,88,106,121,127,134,147,154],{"__ignoreMap":61},[65,66,69,73,77,81,85],"span",{"class":67,"line":68},"line",1,[65,70,72],{"class":71},"sWyjQ","function",[65,74,76],{"class":75},"sj_SG"," sayHello",[65,78,80],{"class":79},"sMAXC","(",[65,82,84],{"class":83},"s_sBn","name",[65,86,87],{"class":79},") {\n",[65,89,91,94,97,99,103],{"class":67,"line":90},2,[65,92,93],{"class":79},"  console.",[65,95,96],{"class":75},"log",[65,98,80],{"class":79},[65,100,102],{"class":101},"sTRMh","'Say'",[65,104,105],{"class":79},");\n",[65,107,109,112,115,118],{"class":67,"line":108},3,[65,110,111],{"class":71},"  return",[65,113,114],{"class":101}," 'Hello'",[65,116,117],{"class":71}," +",[65,119,120],{"class":79}," name;;\n",[65,122,124],{"class":67,"line":123},4,[65,125,126],{"class":79},"}\n",[65,128,130],{"class":67,"line":129},5,[65,131,133],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":132},true,"\n",[65,135,137,140,142,145],{"class":67,"line":136},6,[65,138,139],{"class":75},"sayHello",[65,141,80],{"class":79},[65,143,144],{"class":101},"'Ray'",[65,146,105],{"class":79},[65,148,150],{"class":67,"line":149},7,[65,151,153],{"class":152},"sQrFR","\u002F\u002F Say\n",[65,155,157],{"class":67,"line":156},8,[65,158,159],{"class":152},"\u002F\u002F Hello Ray\n",[12,161,162,163,165],{},"我們可以看到 ",[51,164,139],{}," 這個函式會將結果輸出到 console tab 兩次，那...為什麼這樣算是一個 Side Effect 呢？",[12,167,168,169,171,172,174,175,178],{},"我們剛剛呼叫了 ",[51,170,139],{}," 這個函式，但是它的運算 or 執行結果是不能影響到外層的，而 ",[51,173,139],{}," 這個函式在執行後卻發生會輸出結果到「本身函式之外」，而這也就是為什麼 ",[51,176,177],{},"console.log"," 本身就是一個 Side Effect。",[12,180,181],{},"請注意一件事情，就算這個運算行為或者是執行動作不是包在函式內，只要會更改原始值都算是一個 Side Effect",[56,183,185],{"className":58,"code":184,"language":60,"meta":61,"style":61},"var myName = 'Ray';\n\nmyName = 'Array';\n",[51,186,187,204,208],{"__ignoreMap":61},[65,188,189,192,195,198,201],{"class":67,"line":68},[65,190,191],{"class":71},"var",[65,193,194],{"class":79}," myName ",[65,196,197],{"class":71},"=",[65,199,200],{"class":101}," 'Ray'",[65,202,203],{"class":79},";\n",[65,205,206],{"class":67,"line":90},[65,207,133],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":132},[65,209,210,213,215,218],{"class":67,"line":108},[65,211,212],{"class":79},"myName ",[65,214,197],{"class":71},[65,216,217],{"class":101}," 'Array'",[65,219,203],{"class":79},[12,221,222],{},"意想不到吧？連這種我們常認為理所當然的重新賦予值的行為都算是 Side Effect 的一種，因此 Side Effect 在 JavaScript 中非常常見",[224,225,226,230,233,240],"ul",{},[227,228,229],"li",{},"AJAX",[227,231,232],{},"DOM 操作",[227,234,235,236,239],{},"時間相關操作(",[51,237,238],{},"setTimeout",")",[227,241,242],{},"修改外部參數\n..等等",[12,244,245,246,248],{},"怕了吧，我們常見的開發行為都有 Side Effect 的存在，那麼這不代表叫你只要有 Side Effect 的東西就通通不要使用，而是應該要去理解並且釐清它的運作，這樣子才可以避免一些無法預期的問題，否則你難道要連 ",[51,247,177],{}," 都不用嗎？（笑",[12,250,251,252,257],{},"那麼早期我有寫一篇「",[253,254,256],"a",{"href":255},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20210424\u002F616364031\u002F","什麼是 ESM(ES6 Modules or JavaScript Modules) 呢？","」裡面就有提到一個 Side Effect 模組的部分，因此適當使用 Side Effect 以及了解 Side Effect 是可以幫助開發的。",[19,259,261],{"id":260},"pure-non-pure-function-純與不純的函式","Pure & Non-Pure Function (純與不純的函式)",[12,263,264],{},"Pure Function 中文又稱之為純粹函式、純函式，什麼是 Pure Function 呢？",[12,266,267,268,239],{},"開始之前，人家都說好的不學，壞的學特別快 (",[269,270,271],"del",{},"所以就讓我們先來學壞的",[273,274,276],"h3",{"id":275},"non-pure-function-不純函式","Non-Pure Function (不純函式)",[12,278,279],{},"Non-Pure Function，也就是不純的函式，那什麼是不純的函式呢？讓我們看一段簡單的 Non-Pure Function Example Code：",[56,281,283],{"className":58,"code":282,"language":60,"meta":61,"style":61},"var myName =  'Ray';\n\nfunction sayHello() {\n  console.log('Hello' + myName);\n}\n\nsayHello();\n",[51,284,285,298,302,311,327,331,335],{"__ignoreMap":61},[65,286,287,289,291,293,296],{"class":67,"line":68},[65,288,191],{"class":71},[65,290,194],{"class":79},[65,292,197],{"class":71},[65,294,295],{"class":101},"  'Ray'",[65,297,203],{"class":79},[65,299,300],{"class":67,"line":90},[65,301,133],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":132},[65,303,304,306,308],{"class":67,"line":108},[65,305,72],{"class":71},[65,307,76],{"class":75},[65,309,310],{"class":79},"() {\n",[65,312,313,315,317,319,322,324],{"class":67,"line":123},[65,314,93],{"class":79},[65,316,96],{"class":75},[65,318,80],{"class":79},[65,320,321],{"class":101},"'Hello'",[65,323,117],{"class":71},[65,325,326],{"class":79}," myName);\n",[65,328,329],{"class":67,"line":129},[65,330,126],{"class":79},[65,332,333],{"class":67,"line":136},[65,334,133],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":132},[65,336,337,339],{"class":67,"line":149},[65,338,139],{"class":75},[65,340,341],{"class":79},"();\n",[12,343,344,345,347,348,351],{},"上面程式碼看起來很正常、很理所當然，但實際上 ",[51,346,139],{}," 這個函式是會直接取用 Global 的變數，而這種狀況我們可能會因為一些操作而導致污染 ",[51,349,350],{},"myName"," 這個變數，因此它是一個 Non-Pure Function，Non-Pure Function 也可能會導致一些 Side Effect 的狀況。",[273,353,355],{"id":354},"pure-function-純函式","Pure Function (純函式)",[12,357,358],{},"那什麼是 Pure Function 呢？如果拿前面的範例來調整的話，就會變成以下：",[56,360,362],{"className":58,"code":361,"language":60,"meta":61,"style":61},"function sayHello(name) {\n  return 'Hello' + name;\n}\n\nconst myName = sayHello('Ray');\n",[51,363,364,376,387,391,395],{"__ignoreMap":61},[65,365,366,368,370,372,374],{"class":67,"line":68},[65,367,72],{"class":71},[65,369,76],{"class":75},[65,371,80],{"class":79},[65,373,84],{"class":83},[65,375,87],{"class":79},[65,377,378,380,382,384],{"class":67,"line":90},[65,379,111],{"class":71},[65,381,114],{"class":101},[65,383,117],{"class":71},[65,385,386],{"class":79}," name;\n",[65,388,389],{"class":67,"line":108},[65,390,126],{"class":79},[65,392,393],{"class":67,"line":123},[65,394,133],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":132},[65,396,397,400,404,407,409,411,413],{"class":67,"line":129},[65,398,399],{"class":71},"const",[65,401,403],{"class":402},"sCcAr"," myName",[65,405,406],{"class":71}," =",[65,408,76],{"class":75},[65,410,80],{"class":79},[65,412,144],{"class":101},[65,414,105],{"class":79},[12,416,417],{},"Pure Function 會保持著一個原則，也就是一個輸入 (input) 與輸出 (output)，那這就是一個 Pure Function。",[12,419,420],{},"因此 Pure Function 遵守一個規則也是...",[39,422,423],{},[12,424,425],{},"one input, one output",[19,427,429],{"id":428},"higher-order-function高階函式","Higher-Order Function(高階函式)",[12,431,432],{},"Higher-Order Function 又稱之為 HOF，簡單來講就是函式可以被傳入到其他函式或者是回傳一個函式，只要滿足這兩個條件，那麼它就是一個 Higher-Order Function。",[12,434,435],{},"我知道這邊還是很抽象，所以就來看一些範例程式碼，首先是「函式可以被傳入函式」",[56,437,439],{"className":58,"code":438,"language":60,"meta":61,"style":61},"function fn(callback) {\n  console.log('fn');\n}\n\nfunction HOF(callback) {\n  console.log('HOF');\n  callback();\n}\n\nHOF(fn);\n",[51,440,441,455,468,472,476,489,502,509,513,518],{"__ignoreMap":61},[65,442,443,445,448,450,453],{"class":67,"line":68},[65,444,72],{"class":71},[65,446,447],{"class":75}," fn",[65,449,80],{"class":79},[65,451,452],{"class":83},"callback",[65,454,87],{"class":79},[65,456,457,459,461,463,466],{"class":67,"line":90},[65,458,93],{"class":79},[65,460,96],{"class":75},[65,462,80],{"class":79},[65,464,465],{"class":101},"'fn'",[65,467,105],{"class":79},[65,469,470],{"class":67,"line":108},[65,471,126],{"class":79},[65,473,474],{"class":67,"line":123},[65,475,133],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":132},[65,477,478,480,483,485,487],{"class":67,"line":129},[65,479,72],{"class":71},[65,481,482],{"class":75}," HOF",[65,484,80],{"class":79},[65,486,452],{"class":83},[65,488,87],{"class":79},[65,490,491,493,495,497,500],{"class":67,"line":136},[65,492